ARSHDEEP STRIKES GOLD WITH THE FIRST BALL! Arshdeep Singh bowling to Shayan Jahangir, good length ball, pitching on off stump, Shayan Jahangir  is caught off-guard. The impact on the pad is palpable, and the sound echoes around the stadium, and Up goes the Finger!  India draw first blood
